This guide makes several references to &quot;OLR&quot;. This is short for &quot;off-line reader&quot; and is used in this guide to describe all OLRs (e.g. AmiQWK), tossers (e.g. Foozle) and message readers (e.g. Spot).  

Tag-o-Miga is @{"b"}PostcardWare@{"ub"}! If you decide to use Tag-o-Miga regularly you must read the section in the licence agreement. Thank you.  Introductions       
    	
